    lyrics: `[VERSE 1]
No Raider key in my pack, I cut out wide
Past Pattern House stone, where the hillsides hide
See a flare punch up, red burn in the night
Hanging over north complex like a warning light
I dive into cover, keep my head down,
Sweeping the hillside to smoke out that clown.

[PRE-CHORUS 1]
