  {
    title: 'Dam Goblin',
    lyrics: `[VERSE 1]
Less than ten minutes, let's get to work,
Edge of the map where the smart ones lurk.
Flares going up like a blood-red storm,
We stay cold, let the heroes perform.

You dive mid, we stay wide,
Watch your bodies from the mountainside.
You chase fame, we chase scraps,
You die loud, we run laps.

[PRE-CHORUS]
Hear the countdown, feel that drag,
Every death's another bag.
You respawn, we take notes,
Mark the ground with fallen goats.

[CHORUS]
DAM GOBLIN!!
Last ten minutes, crawling out the dark.
DAM GOBLIN!!
Keys in hand while you're bones in the park.

DAM GOBLIN!!
You paint the dam with your brave last stand.
DAM GOBLIN!!
We just slide in, loot still warm in our hands.

[VERSE 2]
Dam Control Center, tower door hums,
All your risk in our low-life thumbs.
Testing Annex, lights gone dead,
We walk through where you all bled.

Staff Room, lockers, pockets picked,
Every brave push makes us rich.
Surveillance Key in the final glow,
Replay your deaths on a private show.

[PRE-CHORUS]
You took bullets, we took time,
You dropped gear, we dropped pride.
Call us rats, we don't care,
You're the reason there's loot in there.

[CHORUS]
DAM GOBLIN!!
Last ten minutes, crawling out the dark.
DAM GOBLIN!!
Keys in hand while you're bones in the park.
DAM GOBLIN!!
You paint the dam with your brave last stand.
DAM GOBLIN!!
We just slide in, loot still warm in our hands.

[BRIDGE]
Wait / wait / wait / then we eat,
Let the flares mark every treat.
You burn out, we cash in,
Lowest of the low with a greedy grin.

[FINAL CHORUS]
DAM GOBLIN!!
Last ten minutes, hear that clock choke out.
DAM GOBLIN!!
All your highlights feeding our loadout.

DAM GOBLIN!!
You fight fair, we fight smart in the grime.
DAM GOBLIN!!
See you on the killfeed, thanks for your time.

DAM GOBLIN!! … DAM GOBLIN!!`,
